headline: Zoetis Highlights R&D Leadership and Long-Term Growth Opportunity at Innovation Webcast
summary: PARSIPPANY, N.J., December 02, 2025--Zoetis Inc. (NYSE: ZTS), the world’s leading animal health company, will host an Innovation Webcast today at 8:30 a.m. ET to provide an update on its proven innovation model, robust and diversified R&D pipeline, and upcoming growth catalysts as the company continues pioneering the future of animal health.
